              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">2</span>
                Analisis hasil per siswa atau per kelompok
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">3</span>
                Gunakan visualisasi untuk insight yang lebih baik
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">4</span>
                Download laporan lengkap untuk dokumentasi
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8">
            <i class="fas fa-video text-[#0174BE] text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4 select-none"></i>
            <h2 class="text-[#0C356A] font-semibold text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2 select-none">Implementasi Rekomendasi</h2>
            <p class="text-[#0C356A] text-xs sm:text-sm mb-6 select-none">
              Panduan menerapkan hasil analisis dalam strategi pengajaran
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#0C356A] text-xs sm:text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">1</span>
                Identifikasi siswa yang memerlukan intervensi
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">2</span>
                Buat rencana pembelajaran yang disesuaikan
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">3</span>
                Monitor progress secara berkala
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span
                  class="flex-shrink-0 bg-[#FFC436] text-[#0C356A] font-semibold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 select-none">4</span>
                Evaluasi efektivitas intervensi
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Pengenalan Fitur Lengkap Section -->
      <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 sm:py-12">
        <h1 class="text-center font-extrabold text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-8 sm:mb-10 text-[#0C356A]">Pengenalan Fitur
          Lengkap</h1>

        <section
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 mb-8 sm:mb-10 shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-transparent">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-base sm:text-lg mb-2 text-[#0C356A]">Prediksi Nilai Siswa</h2>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm mb-4 text-[#0C356A]">
            Menggunakan algoritma regresi untuk memprediksi nilai akhir siswa berdasarkan data historis, kehadiran, dan
            faktor-faktor lain yang mempengaruhi pembelajaran.
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-3 text-[#0C356A] text-sm sm:text-base">Manfaat Utama:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-[#0C356A]">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
